    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine yourself gliding down the coast at sunset, the golden hour reflecting off the deep, lustrous finish of this automotive masterpiece. This car doesn't just transport you; it transports the very air around it, turning heads with a silent, dignified grace that modern vehicles simply cannot replicate. Every stitch in the supple leather tells a story of craftsmanship, and the engine\u2019s purr is a soothing reminder of a time when cars were built with soul. This is more than a purchase; it is an inheritance of elegance, a preserved relic of the open road waiting for its next great chapter with you behind the wheel.",
      "price": 48500.0,
