      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute benchmark in automotive preservation. This vehicle arrives in flawless, showroom condition, having been maintained to the most exacting standards. The exterior finish retains its original factory luster, while the interior remains in pristine, untouched state, free from any signs of wear. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure it performs exactly as engineered. For the collector or discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection, this example represents a rare opportunity to own a virtually new vehicle at a significant value. Experience the pinnacle of quality and drive with absolute confidence.",
